Detailed Description

CmdInsertShapeKit class is the insert command for tshapekit nodes stored in the command stack.

CmdInsertShapeKit represents a single tshapekit insertion action on a scene, insert a new tshapekit node to the scene.

TShapeKit *  shapeKit,
SceneModel *  model,
QUndoCommand *  parent = 0 
)

Creates a new shapekit insert command that adds a shapekit node to a node given with the parentIndex node in the model.

If parent is not null, this command is appended to parent's child list and then owns this command.
